<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />復活節開心嗎——？！<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />打起十二分精神<delay8 />在島上走動
就會找到蛋了——！<pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為到處都藏著蛋，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一不小心就錯過了，對吧？<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼，<delay8 />究竟能找到幾顆蛋咧——？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><colour id="3" />蹦蹦<colour id="65535" />那傢伙，<delay20 />
好像一直在注意背後，<delay8 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那傢伙<delay8 />其實是運動員吧——？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看，<delay8 />不是有種運動<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓別人站到自己背後，<delay8 />就算輸了嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道嗎？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實復活節的蛋<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是可以吃的喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是不是覺得它顏色太繽紛，而有所懷疑？<delay40 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈！<delay8 />其實那就是一個蛋形的點心，<delay20 />
不會有問題的——！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">有時候會有格外繽紛的氣球飛過去，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道能用什麼東西將它射下來咧——？<pageBreak /><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />即使是以我超凡的彈跳力，<delay20 />
也沒辦法跳到那麼高，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以讓我很在意耶——！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了，<delay8 />海邊好像漂來<delay20 />
和平常不一樣的瓶中信喔？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你<delay8 />撿到了嗎——？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />打開一看，<delay8 />會有煙霧冒出來，<delay20 />
就在那個瞬間<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />！！<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />開玩笑的啦！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你還是撿到之後<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />自己親眼確認吧——？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="1" />岩石蛋<colour id="65535" />啊，<delay20 />是一種長得很像岩石的蛋，<delay8 />
感覺比其他的蛋還重且硬，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很適合拿來做重量訓練喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />這種蛋不太常見。<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像要使用Nook哩數旅行前往無人島，<delay20 />
在那裡才會有很多這種蛋，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay20 />
蛋<delay8 />找得還順利嗎——？<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，我有個建議喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果<delay8 />你找不太到蛋的話，<delay20 />
就試著敲擊各種不同的樹木吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />特別是椰子樹。<delay20 />
因為椰子樹的硬度和其他的樹木不同，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很適合用來健身喔——！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了，<delay8 />你知道嗎？<delay40 />
這個時期<delay8 />不只可以釣到魚，
還可以釣到蛋喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說回來，<delay8 />釣到的蛋<delay20 />
是什麼魚的蛋啊？<delay40 />
<anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難道是<delay8 />島主的蛋嗎？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>